  "text": "SpyWare [CITATION_1] captures and stores the code changes in a centralised repository in a extremely fine granularity. SpyWare records detailed changes such as a line added in a method, as well as more high-level changes like refactorings. The authors aim at post-mortem comprehension of developer work, while we focused on helping developers for their day-to-day work.",
